settings.title: What is Speaking Roses?
settings.content:
Welcome to Speaking Roses - Where Emotions Blossom in Every Petal.

At the forefront of innovation, we've pioneered and patented a unique flower printing technology, allowing us to inscribe personalized messages and images onto fresh, live blooms. This groundbreaking approach fuses the timeless charm of flowers with the power of human expression, transforming every occasion into an unforgettable memory. Our flower printer replaces traditional paper with the very petals that convey your heartfelt messages. It's a marriage of the greeting card market and the promotional industry, reinventing the way we communicate with the beauty of flowers as our canvas.

settings.title: Where We Have Been
settings.content:
Internationally acclaimed, Speaking Roses has been honored at the International Horti Fair Floral Show in Holland and recognized as the best product by the Promotional Products Association International. Our embossed flowers have graced the hands of Hollywood luminaries, including Tom Cruise, Ellen DeGeneres, and Donald Trump, who have both used and gifted these unique creations.

Our printed flowers have made appearances at prestigious events such as the Kentucky Derby, the Oscars, the Rose Bowl, and the Emmy Awards. Garnering widespread media attention, Speaking Roses has been featured on shows like Access Hollywood and E! Entertainment, as well as in over 100 renowned publications, including Forbes, Family Circle, In Touch, and Inc. Join us in the art of floral expression, where each blossom becomes a canvas for your heartfelt sentiments.

settings.homepage_text_under_banner: Watch the excitement as Tom Cruise wows the audience by personally giving every woman on the Ellen DeGeneres Show a Speaking Roses bouquet for Mother's Day!
